lyTime":"2019-09-19T12:15:36.000Z","msg":"FF如果有日好多人發緊夢 襯警力集中哂某一區 我襯果度人少少唔小心入咗去然後唔小心影咗相 拍埋片 似乎代價唔算好大 如果有方法可以夾硬出返嚟嘅話<br />\n<br />\n《簡易程序治罪條例》 ── 第4條 在公眾地方犯的妨擾罪等<br />\n任何人無合法權限或解釋而 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(30)侵入或容許獸類侵入歸屬於公職人員或公共機關，或由公職人員或公共機關管轄或管理的任何宅院、物業單位、墓地或土地；<br />\n<br />\n可處罰款$500或監禁3個月。"},{"pid":"f2f2cb2b701313b76f50482cbdfffed43a844d75","tid":1576150,"uid":270863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:16:36.000Z","msg":"推爆佢啦！"},{"pid":"58b2035ff595d12551210b0f82be732cc690ff32","tid":1576150,"uid":175110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:45:15.000Z","msg":"新屋嶺冇人理，咪只理太子，新屋死人比太子可能仲多"},{"pid":"7cc471cf64654fe6177f92a1c83e1c8fe53dae06","tid":1576150,"uid":320795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58b2035ff595d12551210b0f82be732cc690ff32","tid":1576150,"uid":175110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:45:15.000Z","msg":"新屋嶺冇人理，咪只理太子，新屋死人比太子可能仲多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:45:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c765adda97648882f2cfc5c097dd6d441bc02c","tid":1576150,"uid":269166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T10:33:42.000Z","msg":"重要救命請廣傳！<br />\n<br />\n如果大家真係不幸被捕入咗新屋嶺，係俾人瘋狂毆打嘅時候，要不停大叫自己親人名字同聯絡電話，因為有可能有返一兩個小有惻隱之心嘅差佬，會暗中致電你嘅親友，通知你屋企人你喺新屋嶺！<br />\n<br />\n已經有一個朋友嘅老公係咁樣被救出（不過當事人情況非常嚴重，而且出現精神問題，不停喺家中大叫及食唔到野瞓唔到覺，因為入邊虐待得非常利害，你係會不停聽到慘叫尖叫凄厲嘅哭聲，其中一樣係日夜毒打、比屎撈飯佢哋食！）。<br />\n<br />\n最重要嘅講明，打佢哋、虐待佢哋嘅，全部都係流利廣東話嘅香港差佬，所以唔好再幻想係公安或者武警做！<br />\n<br />\n香港嘅共匪走狗就係咁仆街賤格！<br />\n<br />\n但最緊要係救到人出嚟，非常重要請大家廣傳！<br />\n<br />\n#一定要血債血償<br />\n<br />\n#黑警絕對要死全家<br />\n<br />\n#香港國民軍<br />\n<br />\nFrom FB解放香港<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/114726626568147/posts/129985468375596?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F114726626568147%2Fposts%2F129985468375596%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2F4Vo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=b231093e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/114726626568147/posts/129985468375596?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"77a2798e3b9d74dd3c57bacdc4a707593fb54e91","tid":1576150,"uid":326323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e66b34e21090e56d936c1bfbfa70f60da00af2ab","tid":1576150,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:14:56.000Z","msg":"[遊行]點解我地咁多人 唔搞一次新屋嶺遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1576132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1576132</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T23:51:37.000Z","msg":"唔可以？？？？一定唔好去，，因為走唔到出來，相比狗捉"},{"pid":"fdc3a54ada83b5c48858ebc3423af0421575e0a5","tid":1576150,"uid":297686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:06:44.000Z","msg":"其實有無手足聽到d狗用國語溝通？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}